{"tid":32322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃台仰　離港赴台出席　世界人權日活動","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:18:10.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e72d6dcfeeaab6d9ee6d37cf897cf5f84f55277","tid":32322,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/12/ray-wong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F12%2Fray-wong%2F&d=smYIAVCoBVBp%2BjayXsyke3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=17c822cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/12/ray-wong/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1209_ray.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F1209_ray.jpg&h=cbb4b767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在農曆年初旺角衝突中，被控參與非法暴動的本土民主前線發言人黃台仰，早前申請更改保釋條件短暫離開香港，高等法院今日（九日）在控方不反對下，批准他今日起至本月十八日離港。他表示，將代表本民前到台灣參加世界人權日嘉年華的會議及公開活動。<br />\n<br />\n黃台仰及本民前另一發言人梁天琦，以及另外八名男子，分別被控參與及煽動暴動等罪名，案件已排期至二零一八年一月十五日開審。"}]}